      <title>研究称瑞士央行应将利润直接分配给公民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/snb-should-distribute-profits-directly-to-citizens-study-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士一家亲市场智库表示，瑞士央行应该将其利润直接分配给公民，以便在决定发放多少利润时不受政治因素影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/snb-should-distribute-profits-directly-to-citizens-study-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:02:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
